### What to do when new release of NuTyX is done:
1. The nutyx package

   1.1 commit the <new_version> archive for the nutyx package.
   1.2 Build the <new_version> version of the nutyx package.

2. NuTyX Background

   2.1 if major release updade, adjust background picture in glib, slim, lxdm and plasma-framework
   2.2 Adjust the slim and lxdm background with the <new_version> string

3. install-nutyx script

   3.1 Replace install-nutyx with the latest one for nutyx package on nutyx.org/install-nutyx
   3.2 adjust the md5sum signature of the install-nutyx script in place

4. NuTyX_<arch>_..._<new_version>.iso

   4.1 the fixed BASE ISO in 64 bits
   4.2 the rolling BASE ISO in 64 bits
   4.2 the rolling MATE ISO in 64 bits
   4.3 the rolling BASE ISO in 32 bits

5. forum.nutyx.org and forums.nutyx.org (obsolet)

   5.1 Change the registration validation string on both forums
   5.2 Adjust the news with the <new_version> iso link

6. nutyx.org

   6.1 Copy existing <lang>/contents/news to <lang>/old-news/<Year-Mounth-Day>.html
   6.2 Make the news in english and in french with following points

        NuTyX <new_version> available with cards <version>

        Main update packages list
        Liste des mises à jour principales

        Upgrade procedure
        Procédure de mise à jour
        Specifics to this version
        Points spécifiques à cette version

        Olds news
        Anciennes nouvelles

  6.3 Replace  the <old_version> string to <new_version> string on nutyx.org website on every concerned pages
  6.4 Adjust the download page

7. GIT:

   7.1 Create new tags with <new_version> for packages-x86_64 and packages-i686
   7.2 Delete existing branch fixed and create new ones at latest tags <new_version> for packages-x86_64 and packages-i686

8. download.nutyx.org

    8.1 adjust Package List on nutyx.org
    8.2 Send everything on the download.nutyx.org mirror

9  fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/NuTyX

    9.1 adjust the <new_version> and date of the NuTyX
    9.2 add news features if applicable

10  Mailling List

    10.1 Send the news to the nutyx.annonce@nutyx.org
